## Write a program to convert minutes to days

1 day = 24 hours = 1440 minutes

```txt
Input  : 7200
Output : 5
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-minutes-to-days" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main()
{
    int minutes;
    printf("Enter Minutes   :   ");
    scanf("%i", &minutes);

    int days = minutes / 1440;

    printf("Days    :   %i", days);
    return 0;
}
```

